name: Tenyi Dragon Vishudda
desc: If you control no Effect Monsters: You can Special Summon this card from your hand. If you control a face-up non-Effect Monster: You can banish this card from your hand or GY, then target 1 card your opponent controls; return it to the hand. You can only use each effect of "Tenyi Dragon Vishudda" once per turn.
str2: Target 1 card to return to hand
